                <supplied reason="lost">Rufiu</supplied>s <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Messala <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> praefectus urbi <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">ad omne</supplied><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> splendorem publicum in vico patricio <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">simulacrum</supplied> Victoriae <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">poni iussit</supplied> et fieri et ornari procurabit <note>sic</note>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist heute verschollen. Ergänzungsvorschlag nach G. Alföldy u. S. Orlandi.</p>
